---
title: Sticky Beef Rice Bowl with Jasmine Rice, Green Beans and Peanuts
description: This Sticky Beef Rice Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-beef-rice-bowl-2e86ac7d-84675b93.jpg
